      <div class='locations-blog'>
        <h4>Las Vegas</h4>
        <div class='vegas-div'>
            <img class='vegas-img' src='https://pix10.agoda.net/hotelImages/75/-1/450838815fb602d9fe58bba500a04a84.jpg?s=1024x768'>
            <img class='vegas-img' src='https://cdn.getyourguide.com/img/location/5ffeb496e3e09.jpeg/88.jpg'>
        </div>

        <div class='p-div'>
            <p>Vegas Baby! Here are some of my little tips for visiting the city of lights for the first time.
                <br>
            Hotels! Read the reviews of every hotel you are interested in. Personally, I've only stayed at the New York New York hotel on the strip, and the Stratosphere hotel (now called the STRAT). I really enjoyed New York New York, the room was beautiful, the hotels in the casio were fantastic, and the rollercoaster and game room were a fun little area to spend some time in! Right in the middle of the Strip, it was very quick and easy to sight see and roam around the strip. I really recommend taking a lyft or uber if you want to travel farther down the strip toward the Strat, or even fremont street.
            </p>
            
            <div class='vegas-div'>
                <img class='vegas-img' src='https://1pg6x1158j2c3wpy0512zgcs-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/upgraded-viva-vision-17.jpg'>
                <img class='vegas-img' src='https://media2.trover.com/T/5d2350db6e1f1f4ef8006af5/fixedw.jpg'>
            </div>
            <br>
            <p>When in Vegas, Have some Fun! At the Strat, I experienced the Sky Jump. It was very thrilling and fun, if you want a quick thrilling experience, the Sky jump is definetly for you. I made the mistake of walking the 4.5 miles from New York New York to the Strat hotel, in sandles without sunscreen. Don't make the same mistake as I did, take the uber and save yourself some feet pain and sunburns! While touring the strip, make sure to walk through each hotels casino. There are some incredible decor in the strip hotels, theyre definetly worth seeing.</p>
        </div>
